{"id": "ros032", "name": "Audio_Kyuu_702_12_15_3", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>All in all, both of you should be exhausted. I am very thankful that you're still willing to stay here. Please get some rest. I must now go back to clean up this mess.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "Wheelchair moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Chief, about Miss Pauline's body... we've got everything arranged and ready to go.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "We've also contacted those in Node 08 who are affected by this, including Luis Pauline, Joe Miller and all her known friends on the list. Her father will apply for a temporary parole from the restricted area so he can organize his daughter's funeral.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... What about the public announcement? Miss Pauline is considered a celebrity figure in Node 08.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Yes. We've dealt with all the issues regarding the agency through our connections. This is the press release; death by accident. No mention of the organization what so ever.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Chief... are you alright...?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I'm... feeling a bit tired. Can I leave you in charge of the clean up for now?</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Certainly! But what about you...\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>The priority is to repair the defenses in area 03. Within two hours, I want a written report with all the damages listed on it.</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "Chief... are you really alright...?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Can you do it?</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "... Yes.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "Wheelchair moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Member D"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Chief...</font>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......!\nNora...</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "Wheelchair moving"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......\nNora, question: Miss Cherry...</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>You fixed all these instruments...</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......\nAffirmative.</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......\nWhy...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Answer: Nora, has dreams of music. This unit, saw broken instruments. This unit, hopes Nora can...</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Why did you come back?</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>This unit, wants to protect Nora.</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Nora...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Miss Pauline... is dead.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I... couldn't do it. I was unable to recover the power in time. I caused her death.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Not Nora's fault. This unit...</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Do you think... it's your fault?</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......\n... Unable to analyze.</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... That's because your emotions are a lot more complicated than you think.</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>I... I don't know anymore. What is right? What is wrong?</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>When I couldn't destroy you, it felt... painful. Was I... crying back then? I thought I was experiencing my own emotions... for the first time since that incident——Yet after seeing Miss Pauline, I was still able to handle everything so calmly...</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Nora...</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Tell me, ROBO; right now... what do you feel?</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Emotion simulation keyword searching...\nKeywords: self-blame, regret, sadness... anger.</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Is that so? You are me... Then perhaps... that's just how it is, right...? However, we both don't know how to express these emotions, or should I say, that we've both lost this function...</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO, can you... lock the door? I don't want other people... to see my face right now.</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>... Understood.</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>とにかく、疲れたでしょう。\nここに残ってくれてありがとう。\n少し休んでいて。\n私はここの後始末をしてしまうから。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "車いす起動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "ボス、Paulineさんの遺体と……今後の諸々についても手配しました。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "Luis Pauline、Joe Miller、その他友人など、Node08の関係者各位にも連絡しました。\n彼女の父親は、今後の手続きなどのこともあるため、管制区に仮釈放を申請するそうです。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……外への公開は？PaulineさんはNode08では有名人だから。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "はい。\nつてを通して事務所の方の処理も済ませました。\nこれが発表される予定の記事です。\n事故死ということになっています。\n組織のことは一切外に漏れません。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "ボス……大丈夫ですか……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>少し……疲れた。\nここの後始末を任せていい？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "もちろん！でも……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>第3エリアの防衛設備を優先的にお願い。\nそれから2時間以内に損傷箇所のリストを。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "ボス……本当に大丈夫ですか……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>できる？</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……はい。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "車いす起動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……ボス……</font>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……！\nNora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "車いす起動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………Nora。\nクエスチョン：Cherryさんは……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>楽器を修理したの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………\nはい。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>………\nなんで……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>アンサー：Noraは音楽の夢を抱いています。本機は壊れた楽器を見て、Noraが……</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>なんで帰ってきたの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>本機は、Noraを守りたいです。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Nora……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Paulineさんは……死んだ。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>私が……できなかったから。\nすぐに電力を回復させていれば……\n彼女は私が殺したも同然。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……Noraのせいではありません。本機が……</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>あなたは……あなたのせいだと思うの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>………\n……分析できません。</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……それは、あなたの感情があなたの思っているよりも複雑だから。</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>私……もう分からない。\n何が正しいの？何が間違ってるの？</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>あなたを、この手で壊すことができなかったとき……すごくつらかった……私、泣いてた？\n私、あの時以来初めて「感情」ってものを感じることができたと思った……\nでも、Paulineさんのことを見て、それでもあんなに冷静に対応できるなんて……</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ねぇ、ROBO……教えて……\nあなたは……今、どんな気持ち？</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……感情シミュレーション、キーワード検索中……\nキーワード：自責、後悔、悲しみ……怒り。</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……そっか。\nあなたは私だから……そうかもしれないね。\nでも、私たちはその感情を表現する方法が分からない。\nもしかしたら……その機能が壊れちゃったのかもね。</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO……鍵をかけてくれる？\nこんなところ……他の人には見られたくない。</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……はい。</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>總之兩位應該都非常疲憊了，我很感謝你們願意繼續留下來，請稍微休息一下吧。我必須回去善後這片狼藉。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，Pauline 小姐的遺體……已經照安排處理好了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "也聯絡了 Node 08 能接應的相關人士，包括名單上的 Luis Pauline、Joe Miller 以及所有已知的友人，他的父親會向管制區申請暫時假釋，好處理女兒的後事。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……對外聲明呢？Pauline 小姐在 Node 08 算小有名氣的公眾人物。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是，我們已經透過關係處理好經紀公司那邊的事，這是講稿，是意外死亡，絲毫不會透漏組織的訊息。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長……您還好嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我……稍微有點累了。損傷的善後能麻煩你先處理嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "當然！倒是您……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>優先修繕第三區的防禦，並在兩小時內列一份損害清單給我。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長……您真的沒事嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>做得到嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……是。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……組長……</font>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……！\nNora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。\nNora，提問：Cherry 小姐……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>你把這些樂器修好了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。\n肯定。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。\n為什麼……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>回答：Nora 有音樂的夢想，本機看到壞掉的樂器，希望 Nora 可以……</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>為什麼要回來？</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>本機，想保護 Nora。</i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Nora……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Pauline 小姐……死了。</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我……下不了手。沒能即時恢復電力，是我害死了她。</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……不是 Nora 的錯，是本機……</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>你覺得……是你的錯嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。\n……無法分析。</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……因為你的情感比你想像的還要複雜。</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我已經……不知道了。什麼是對的？什麼是錯的？</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>下不了手將你摧毀時，好難受……我那是……在哭嗎？第一次以為體會到自己的情感……打從那次以來——但在看到 Pauline 小姐後，我卻還能那麼冷靜地處理一切……</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>告訴我，ROBO，你現在……有什麼感覺？</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……情感模擬關鍵字檢索中……\n關鍵字：自責、悔恨、悲傷……憤怒。</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……是嗎？你就是我……那也許……就是這樣吧……？但我們都不知道該如何表現這些情感，或者說喪失了這項功能……</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO，可以……把門鎖上嗎？我不想讓其他人看見……我現在這個樣子。</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……了解。</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i> 이곳에 남겠다고 말씀해주셔서 두 분께 진심으로 감사드립니다. 많이 지쳤을 텐데 조금 쉬도록 하세요. 저는 돌아가서 이 난장판을 정리해야만 하니 먼저 가보도록 하죠.</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "휠체어 작동"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "팀장님, Pauline 씨의 시체는... 말씀하신 대로 처리했습니다.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "그리고 명단에 있는 Luis Pauline, Joe Miller를 포함해서 Node 08에 있는 Pauline 씨의 모든 지인들에게 연락을 취했습니다. 그의 부친이 관제구역에 휴가 신청을 내고 딸의 장례를 처리할 것이라고 하더군요.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……언론 발표는? Pauline 씨는 Node 08에서 꽤 유명한 사람이거든.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "네, 아는 사람을 통해 이미 소속사 측에도 손을 써두었습니다. 이건 곧 발표될 기사 원고입니다. 사인은 사고로 처리해두었고 조직에 관한 내용은 일절 언급되지 않았습니다.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "팀장님......\n괜찮으십니까……? \n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>조금……피곤한 것 같군. 뒷정리는 우선 네게 맡겨도 될까?</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "물론입니다! 그럼 팀장님은……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>3구역 방어 시스템을 우선적으로 복구시키도록. 그리고 2시간 내에 파손 정도가 얼마나 되는지 작성해서 바로 보고해주고.</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "팀장님.....\n정말 괜찮으신 겁니까……? \n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>할 수 있겠지?</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "……알겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "휠체어 가동"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["조직원 D"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……팀장님……</font>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……!\nNora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "휠체어 가동"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……\nNora, 질문이 있습니다: Cherry 씨는……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>이 악기들, 전부 수리해놨군……</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i> ......\n그렇습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i> ......\n왜...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>대답: Nora는 음악에 대한 꿈을 가지고 있습니다. 그래서 본 기기는 부서진 악기를 보았을 때, Nora가 꼭 그 꿈을...</i>\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>왜 돌아온 거야?</i>\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>본 기기, Nora를 지켜주고 싶습니다. </i>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": " ......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>Nora……? </i>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Pauline 씨는……죽었어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……! \n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>내가...... 제대로 손을 쓰지 못해서... 전력을 즉시 회복시키지 못했어. 나 때문에 죽은 거야.</i>\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……Nora의 잘못이 아닙니다. 그건 본 기기의 잘못...</i>\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>네 잘못이라고…… 그렇게 생각하는 거야?</i>\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i> ......\n……분석할 수 없습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……네 감정은 네가 생각한 것보다 훨씬 더 복잡해서 그럴 거야.</i>\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": " ......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>난…… 난 이제 무엇이 옳고 무엇이 그른 지 알 수 없게 돼버렸어.</i>\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": " ......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>너를 내 손으로 차마 파괴하지 못 했을 때... 그때 난... 울고 있었어? 그때 처음으로 나도 감정을 느낄 수 있구나라고 느꼈어... 하지만 Pauline 씨를 봤을 땐, 그런대로 냉정을 유지하고 있었지...</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……Nora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>말해줘, ROBO... 넌 지금... 어떤 감정을 느끼고 있지?</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......감정 시뮬레이션 키워드 검색 중...\n키워드: 자책, 후회, 슬픔... 분노.</i>\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......그래? 너는 나니까……그래서일지도...하지만 우린 둘은 그러한 감정을 표현하는 방법을 모르고 있어. 아니면 그런 기능이 완전히 없어져버린 걸지도  모르지...</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": " ......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO... 문 좀 잠가 줄래? 지금 이 모습을... 다른 사람에게 보이고 싶지 않거든.</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>......알겠습니다.</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>總之兩位應該都非常疲憊了，我很感謝你們願意繼續留下來，請稍微休息一下吧。我必須回去善後這片狼藉。</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長，Pauline 小姐的遺體……已經照安排處理好了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "也聯絡了 Node 08 能接應的相關人士，包括名單上的 Luis Pauline、Joe Miller 以及所有已知的友人，他的父親會向管制區申請暫時假釋，好處理女兒的後事。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……對外聲明呢？Pauline 小姐在 Node 08 算小有名氣的公眾人物。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "是，我們已經透過關係處理好經紀公司那邊的事，這是講稿，是意外死亡，絲毫不會透漏組織的訊息。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長……您還好嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我……稍微有點累了。損傷的善後能麻煩你先處理嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "當然！倒是您……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>優先修繕第三區的防禦，並在兩小時內列一份損害清單給我。</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "組長……您真的沒事嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>做得到嗎？</i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "……是。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["組員 D"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……組長……</font>\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……！\nNora……</i>\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "輪椅驅動"], "content": ""}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ROBO_Head"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。\nNora，提問：Cherry 小姐……</i>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>你把這些樂器修好了……</i>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……。\n肯定。</i>\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。\n為什麼……？</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>回答：Nora 有音樂的夢想，本機看到壞掉的樂器，希望 Nora 可以……</i>\n"}, {"id