rsation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ROBO，可以……把門鎖上嗎？我不想讓其他人看見……我現在這個樣子。</i>\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[ROBO_Head]"], "content": "<i>……了解。</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Nora'sRoom"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>总之两位应该都非常疲惫了，我很感谢你们愿意继续留下来，请稍微休息一下吧。我必须回去善后这片狼藉。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "轮椅驱动"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Store", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "组长，Pauline 小姐的遗体……已经照安排处理好了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "也联络了 Node 08 能接应的相关人士，包括名单上的 Luis Pauline、Joe Miller 以及所有已知的友人，他的父亲会向管制区申请暂时假释，好处理女儿的后事。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……对外声明呢？ Pauline 小姐在 Node 08 算小有名气的公众人物。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "是，我们已经透过关系处理好经纪公司那边的事，这是讲稿，是意外死亡，丝毫不会透漏组织的讯息。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "组长……您还好吗……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我……稍微有点累了。损伤的善后能麻烦你先处理吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "当然！倒是您……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>优先修缮第三区的防御，并在两小时内列一份损害清单给我。 </i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "组长……您真的没事吗……？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>做得到吗？ </i>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["组员 D"], "content": "……是。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_WheelChair", "轮椅驱动"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": [